Holiday data attribution
========================

The holiday dates in `holidays.json` are derived from the
`pandas_market_calendars` Python package and committed to this
repository as static JSON. `pandas_market_calendars` is NOT a
runtime dependency of AIphaForge — only the offline generator
script (`scripts/generate_holidays_json.py`) imports it.

Upstream package: pandas_market_calendars
Upstream URL:     https://github.com/rsheftel/pandas_market_calendars
Upstream license: MIT

The verbatim MIT license text from the upstream project is
reproduced below. Date ranges, calendar selections, and refresh
cadence are recorded under `provenance` in the JSON file.

